ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class focuses on finding the punchline of scientific papers and perfecting presentation skills.

This is a great course and felt like something I would take voluntarily despite it being a requirement. There was a large degree of discussion and scientific discourse, a useful amount of knowledge, and the ability to interact in a small group setting with professors over science that they knew well. This course is definitely worth taking.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class focuses on finding the punchline of scientific papers and perfecting presentation skills...these are both important aspects to our discipline and research.
